title: Start
---
Follow the tree
<<cam-follow Tree>>

Follow the player
<<cam-follow Player>>

Swivel the cam relatvely by 30 -40 50
<<swivel-rel 30 -40 50>>

Set the camera to 0, 0, 0 over 3 seconds
<<swivel-abs 0 0 0 3>>

Move the cam offset over 2 seconds
<<cam-offset-abs 10 21.9 30 2>>

Return to the player with relative offset 1 sec
<<cam-offset-rel -10 -20 -30>>

Anyway, time to get writing!
